main event: A UFO sighting was reported on October 7, 1966, in Century, West Virginia, involving two objects observed for approximately 25 minutes.
interesting points: The objects were observed traveling from northwest to southeast., The objects emitted various colors including red, green, and yellow lights., Witness confirmed that the objects were in sight continuously for the duration of the observation., The witness mentioned no sound was produced by the objects., The conclusion of the report was that there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: a civilian observing the objects with his wife during their travel
